\c 2
\s Inkulumo kaMozisi isaqhubeka
\p
\v 1 Sasesiphenduka, sasuka saya enkangala, indlela yoLwandle oluBomvu, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* kimi; njalo sayibhoda intaba yeSeyiri insuku ezinengi\x + Nani 14.25. Dute. 1.40.\x*.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kimi isithi:
\v 3 Selibhode intaba le okweneleyo; phendukelani lina enyakatho\x + 1.6.\x*.
\v 4 Balaye-ke abantu usithi: Lidabula umngcele wabafowenu, abantwana bakaEsawu\x + Nani 20.14.\x* abahlala eSeyiri\x + Gen. 32.3.\x*. Njalo bazalesaba, ngakho lizinanzelele kakhulu,
\v 5 lingalwi labo; ngoba kangiyikulinika okwelizwe labo, lelingangokunyathela kwangaphansi konyawo\x + 2.9,19,24.\x*, ngoba ngimnikile uEsawu intaba yeSeyiri ibe yilifa\x + Gen. 32.3.\x*.
\v 6 Lizathenga ukudla kubo ngemali ukuze lidle, lithenge kubo lamanzi ngemali ukuze linathe.
\v 7 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikubusisile emsebenzini wonke wesandla sakho; iyazi ukuhamba kwakho kulinkangala enkulu. Le iminyaka engamatshumi amane iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ibilawe, kawuswelanga lutho\x + 8.2-4.\x*.
\v 8 Uba sisedlula sisuka kubafowethu, abantwana bakaEsawu abahlala eSeyiri\x + Hlu. 11.18.\x*, ngendlela yegceke sisuke eElathi\x + 1 Kho. 9.26. 2 Kho. 14.22. 16.6. 2 Lan. 26.2.\x* njalo sisuka eEziyoni-Geberi\x + Nani 33.35.\x*, saphenduka, sadlula ngendlela yenkangala yakoMowabi.
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Ungahlukuluzi uMowabi, ungalwi labo empini; ngoba kangiyikukunika okwelizwe labo kube yilifa\x + 2.9,19,24.\x*, ngoba ngibanikile abantwana bakaLothi iAri\x + 2.18,29. Nani 21.15.\x* ibe yilifa\x + Gen. 19.36,37.\x*.
\v 10 Kwakuhlala khona endulo amaEmi, abantu abakhulu, labanengi, labade\x + Gen. 14.5.\x*, njengamaAnaki\x + Nani 13.22.\x*;
\v 11 babebalwa \add njenge\add*ziqhwaga labo njengamaAnaki, kodwa amaMowabi ababiza ngokuthi ngamaEmi\x + 2.20; Dute. 3.11,13. Gen. 14.5.\x*.
\v 12 LamaHori ayehlala eSeyiri endulo\x + 2.22; Gen. 14.6.\x*, kodwa abantwana bakaEsawu bawakhupha emfuyweni yabo, bawachitha phambi kwabo, bahlala endaweni yawo, njengokwenza kukaIsrayeli elizweni lelifa lakhe, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyabanika lona\x + Nani 21.24,31,35.\x*.
\v 13 Khathesi, sukumani lina lichaphe isifula iZeredi. Ngakho sachapha isifula iZeredi\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*.
\v 14 Lensuku esahamba ngazo sisuka eKadeshi-Bhaneya\x + 1.19.\x* saze sachapha isifula iZeredi zaziyiminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lesificaminwembili, kwaze kwaphela isizukulwana sonke samadoda empi sisuka phakathi kwenkamba, njengokufunga kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuwo\x + Nani 14.33,35. 26.64. 1.34,35. Hlab. 78.33. 95.11. 106.26. Hez. 20.15.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba isibili isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* sasimelene lawo, ukuwachitha esuka phakathi kwenkamba, aze aphela.
\p
\v 16 Kwasekusithi lapho wonke amadoda empi esephelile esifa esuka phakathi kwabantu,
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kimi isithi:
\v 18 Lamuhla uzakwedlula iAri, umngcele wakoMowabi,
\v 19 lapho ususondele maqondana labantwana bakoAmoni, ungabahlukuluzi, ungalwi labo, ngoba kangiyikukunika okwelizwe labantwana bakoAmoni kube yilifa\x + 2.9,19,24.\x*, ngoba ngilinike abantwana bakaLothi libe yilifa\x + Gen. 19.36,38.\x*.
\v 20 Lalelo labalwa njengelizwe leziqhwaga. Iziqhwaga zahlala kulo endulo, kodwa amaAmoni bazibiza ngokuthi ngamaZamuzumu\x + 2.11.\x*;
\v 21 abantu abakhulu, labanengi, labade, njengamaAnaki; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yabachitha phambi kwabo, babakhupha emfuyweni yabo, bahlala endaweni yabo\x + 1.10.\x*,
\v 22 njengalokho eyakwenzela abantwana bakaEsawu, ababehlala eSeyiri, lapho yawachitha amaHori esuka phambi kwabo, bawakhupha emfuyweni yabo, bahlala endaweni yawo kuze kube lamuhla\x + 2.12.\x*.
\v 23 LamaAvi, ayehlala eHazerimi\x + Josh. 13.3.\x* kuze kube seGaza\x + Gen. 10.19.\x*; amaKafitori, aphuma eKafitori, awachitha, ahlala endaweni yawo\x + Gen. 10.14.\x*.
\v 24 Sukumani, lisuke\x + 2.13.\x* lichaphe isifula iArinoni. Bona, nginikele esandleni sakho uSihoni, inkosi yeHeshiboni, umAmori, lelizwe lakhe\x + Nani 21.13,14. Hlu. 11.18,21.\x*; qala ukudla ilifa lalo, ulwe laye empini\x + Eks. 15.14,15. Dute. 11.25. Josh. 2.9.\x*.
\v 25 Lamuhla ngizaqalisa ukufaka uvalo ngawe lokwesabeka kwakho phezu kobuso bezizwe, ngaphansi kwamazulu wonke, ezizakuzwa umbiko ngawe, zithuthumele, ziqhaqhazele ngenxa yakho\x + Eks. 15.14,15. Dute. 11.25. Josh. 2.9.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Ngasengithuma izithunywa zisuka enkangala yeKedemothi kuSihoni inkosi yeHeshiboni, zilamazwi okuthula, zisithi\x + 20.10.\x*:
\v 27 Ake\x + 2.6; Nani 20.17,19.\x* ngidabule elizweni lakho\x + Nani 21.21,22. Hlu. 11.19.\x*; ngizahamba ngomgwaqo kuphela, ngingaphambukeli ngakwesokunene loba ngakwesokhohlo.
\v 28 Uzangithengisela ukudla ngemali ukuze ngidle, ungiphe amanzi ngemali ukuze nginathe; kuphela ngizadabula ngenyawo zami,
\v 29 njengalokhu abantwana bakaEsawu abahlala eSeyiri lamaMowabi ahlala eAri benza kimi\x + Nani 20.18. Dute. 23.3,4. Hlu. 11.17,18, 5,9.\x*, ngize ngichaphe iJordani, ngingene elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu esinika lona.
\v 30 Kodwa uSihoni inkosi yeHeshiboni kasivumelanga ukuthi sidlule kuye\x + Nani 21.23.\x*; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yenza umoya wakhe waba lukhuni, yenza lenhliziyo yakhe yaba lenkani, ukuze imnikele esandleni sakho, njengalamuhla\x + Eks. 7.3. Eks. 4.21.\x*.
\v 31 IN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kimi: Bona, sengiqalisile ukunikela phambi kwakho uSihoni lelizwe lakhe; qalisa ukudla ilifa, ukuze udle ilifa lelizwe lakhe\x + 2.24.\x*.
\v 32 Kwasekuphuma uSihoni ukumelana lathi, yena labantu bakhe bonke, ukulwa eJahazi\x + Nani 21.23.\x*.
\v 33 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu yasimnikela phambi kwethu\x + 7.2.\x*; sasesimtshaya lamadodana akhe labantu bakhe bonke\x + Nani 21.24. Dute. 29.7.\x*.
\v 34 Ngalesosikhathi sasesithumba yonke imizi yakhe, satshabalalisa wonke umuzi, abesilisa labesifazana labantwanyana; kasitshiyanga insali\x + Levi 27.28,29; Dute. 7.2.\x*;
\v 35 sazithumbela izifuyo kuphela, lempango yemizi esayithumbayo.
\v 36 Kusukela eAroweri esekhunjini lwesifula iArinoni, lomuzi osesifuleni, kuze kube seGileyadi kwakungekho muzi owawuphakeme kakhulu kithi\x + Nani 32.34. Dute. 3.12. 4.48. Josh. 12.2. 13.9,16. 1 Sam. 30.28. 2 Sam. 24.5. 1 Lan. 5.8. Isa. 17.2. Jer. 48.19.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu yayinikela yonke phambi kwethu\x + Hlab. 44.3.\x*.
\v 37 Kuphela kawusondelanga elizweni labantwana bakoAmoni, endaweni yonke yesifula iJaboki, lemizini esezintabeni\x + Nani 21.24. Gen. 32.22.\x*, lakukuphi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu esenqabela khona\x + 2.5,9,19.\x*.